original: intros j i x H. unfold in_interval, interval_union in *. destruct j as [a1 b1]. destruct i as [a2 b2]. simpl in *. apply andb_true_iff in H. apply andb_true_iff. split. - destruct H as [H1 H2]. apply andb_true_iff in H1. apply andb_true_iff in H2. destruct H1 as [H1a H1b]. destruct H2 as [H2a H2b]. apply andb_true_iff. split. + apply Nat.min_glb_iff. split. * apply Nat.min_intro. apply Nat.le_min_l. apply Nat.le_trans with a2; auto. * apply Nat.min_intro. apply Nat.le_min_r. apply Nat.le_trans with a1; auto. + apply Nat.max_lub_iff. split. * apply Nat.max_intro. apply Nat.le_max_l. apply Nat.le_trans with b1; auto. * apply Nat.max_intro. apply Nat.le_max_r. apply Nat.le_trans with b2; auto. - destruct H as [H1 H2]. apply andb_true_iff in H1. apply andb_true_iff in H2. destruct H1 as [H1a H1b]. destruct H2 as [H2a H2b]. apply andb_true_iff. split. + apply Nat.min_glb_iff. split. * apply Nat.min_intro. apply Nat.le_min_l. apply Nat.le_trans with a1; auto. * apply Nat.min_intro. apply Nat.le_min_r. apply Nat.le_trans with a2; auto. + apply Nat.max_lub_iff. split. * apply Nat.max_intro. apply Nat.le_max_l. apply Nat.le_trans with b2; auto. * apply Nat.max_intro. apply Nat.le_max_r. apply Nat.le_trans with b1; auto.
